    "name": "☆Lost Desert Warfare☆ ",
    "roblox_url": "https://www.roblox.com/games/5893623",
    "description": "Finally, it's here. Simply chat \"Jeep\" to regen Unionist Jeep and chat \"Jeep2\" to regen the Nationalist's jeep. More weapons coming soon. Kill each other in a huge war against the other players. To obtain the Rifle gun, you must acheive 5 KOs, to obtain the Sniper Gun, you must achieve 10 KOs. The pistol is a basic starter. Use the Check Health bar at the top to get a precise amount of health. Click the blue Weapons tab next to it to choose your weapon. Click the reset tab if you ever get stuck and wish to spawn again.",
